cockpit-package-manager (0.1.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Package manager interface for Cockpit using PackageKit
  * Features:
    - Browse packages by PackageKit group (cross-distribution compatible)
    - Group list with package counts and installed counts
    - Package list view with search and filtering
    - Detailed package view with dependencies and file lists
    - Install/remove operations with progress tracking
  * Technical implementation:
    - React 18 + TypeScript for UI
    - PatternFly 6 components
    - Comprehensive PackageKit D-Bus integration
    - 79 unit tests with full coverage
  * Designed for HaLOS and other Debian-based systems

 -- Matti Airas <matti.airas@hatlabs.fi>  Mon, 04 Nov 2025 21:00:00 +0200
